collectors.titleDetails: (10 total Queries, 10 of them unique across 1 Connection)

queries.sql: SELECT `users`.*, `city`.`name` as `city_name`, `states`.`name` as `state_name`, CASE WHEN users.role = 3 THEN 'Advocate' WHEN users.role = 4 THEN 'CA' WHEN users.role = 5 THEN 'Adviser' ELSE 'other' END AS role_name FROM `users` LEFT JOIN `city` ON `city`.`id` = `users`.`city` LEFT JOIN `states` ON `states`.`id` = `users`.`state` WHERE `users`.`status` = 1 AND `users`.`role` IN (2) AND `users`.`is_delete` = 0 ORDER BY `users`.`id` DESC LIMIT 50
